org.symphonyoss.symphony.clients

Interface DataFeedClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataFeedClientImpl

    public interface DataFeedClient
    Provides access to datafeed in order to stream all message events (messages) through blocking calls. Created by Frank Tarsillo on 5/15/2016.
